column5: The big crappies are starting to move in...........
Good for you, Larry. Great pic too!
Is this through the ice or softwater? Just wondering. Very nice fish though. I don't think ive caught one over 12" in a very long time
I always hate to see the end of ice fishing season but LOVE the start of sooo many others!! Especially crappie!!  Thanks for getting us warmed up!
